HEADWORD: in-between
<hw>in-between</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>being neither at the beginning
nor at the end in a series or time sequence; <as>as, adolescence is an
awkward <ex>in-between</ex> age</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mediate, middle.</syn>⟦br⟧
